➜重庆火锅！底料每日现炒！
http://www.sohu.com/a/419083856_100131509	47110
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/1423215f95f0494b9674e302e1b4043e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/213047f2b490431e9ff22e1ecc6befdd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>···</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这家店太“轴”了吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>辣椒要从重庆运、锅底非要自己炒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">来广州5年，回头客重庆人占一半</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/3ce48bfc8bcd4e16a07ba35a9bccb4ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
